ShortName: Maximum a posteriori estimation
Topic: statistical-inference
Concepts: MAP estimate (the mode of the posterior — "most probable parameter value given the data AND the prior"), MAP as MLE + prior penalty (optimize log-likelihood plus log-prior), MAP-ridge equivalence (Gaussian prior $\to$ ridge penalty), MAP-lasso equivalence (Laplace prior $\to$ lasso penalty)
BuildsOn: [likelihood-and-log-likelihood](likelihood-and-log-likelihood/lesson.qmd), [priors-posteriors-and-updating](priors-posteriors-and-updating/lesson.qmd), [ridge-regularization](ridge-regularization/lesson.qmd)
UsedBy: —
